reviewText:
Hyperdimension Neptune!

-The best game with anime characters in steam

if you are a fan of J-RPG with battles in turn and anime girls. That game is highly recommended for you!

- Simple gameplay and addictive;
- Very good battle sytem;
- Powerful anime appeal;
- Vibrant soundtrack;
- Many references the world of consoles and animes.

Don't waste your time. Buy this game now!
